short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Cross-reference token IDs of OpenSea NFT collections to determine whether an NFT is mutated or not.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Activate this extension to quickly see which DOGC have been mutated or not. Works exclusively on the Doge Club OpenSea collection. Created by AdioKing.
